Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:07.87,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我没有停止想念的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:14.67,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷惘的心　希望能传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:19.37,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这月光下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:24.87,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:31.27,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一定会去见你　无论你在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:37.67,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个讨厌的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我叫出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被干掉的是你　放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又潮湿又阴暗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和这个已经腐烂的城市正相配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是久良泽凯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个私立侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直旁观着人们那阴暗潮湿的侧面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能够相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所爱之物只有香烟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗喵～太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么噗喵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个贫乳女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才那些发言　可是性骚扰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.26,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟味　脚气药味　还混着些其它的什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有狐臭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊　已经不是可以悠闲的时候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天有人来收接收费啦　电视的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去不久就真的会被停的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法还能看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰的莫里斯可不能落下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是动画啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说会在工作场所看动画的你又算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一开始就定了这个条件的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是这样　琪可才不会在这种腐烂的地方工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女人　而且是美女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.46,0:05:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓侦探的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个你吃了多少苦头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以被骗啊　老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被骗也行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　应该说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想被骗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是委托我们工作…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.06,0:05:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　除此之外还会有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如　来讨贷款之类的很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个…是找猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对　我和柚木…我先生一直都像疼孩子一样疼爱它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小咪不见了　我觉得无法跟柚木交代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您的丈夫现在还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　非常抱歉　我先生几年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦　那实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很理解您的情况以及心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找人倒还好说　找猫实在是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是为难您了吧　委托侦探先生这种工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　其实也不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找狗倒还好说　找猫实在是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十万…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会事先支付一半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算您找不到　也不需要返还了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我们去找小咪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干吗自作主张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请交给久良泽侦探事务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胃口选手吗　不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讨厌猫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了　现在不是考虑你好恶的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀　原化妆品公司员工坠楼死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次也发生过啊　这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察正沿着自杀这条线进行搜查…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了　快去做找猫的广告宣传单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着宣传单  忽悠附近的小孩子去找也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做的事像山一样多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是同一个公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得有点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有听琪可的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是连续自杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都是原『费奥列化妆品』的员工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费奥列化妆品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…啊　我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个香水　是费奥列的超高级品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个要找猫的寡妇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那味道不是很浓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确很浓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个　我们还有不得不干的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说　你看见刚才那位大哥了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吃大喝的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个绝对会胖的　过了三十岁绝对会胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙哦　很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁骨那里真是不能错过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗　费尔南多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理花　你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很忙　别到处乱晃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了　费尔南多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　多谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是别人难得的好心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费尔南多斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个看上去似乎很像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是鼻子稍微有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子不是黑的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐我的cosplay照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.04,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给　谢谢大家喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　你在干什么啊　人家还在认真的找猫的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种是女人和小孩的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信　在这时代你居然说这种差别待遇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是怕猫而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查到了一些有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那个寡妇　她死去的丈夫曾担任费奥列化妆品的要职
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个连续自杀事件的死者也是该化妆品公司的原员工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得线索连起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了　琪可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这种不惹人注意的接点找出事件的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是侦探的真髓　男人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　大家　能让姐姐看猫咪喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:22.40,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,470)\fs34}第七话　山栀子香散五月雨…（前篇）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栀子花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫久良泽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　我今天和这里的夫人有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷和孙女的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是太过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起　让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起的收藏品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是香水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是柚木的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已故的丈夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.49,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木朔太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说他曾担任费奥列化妆品的要职
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从调香开始起家的　所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对香味很敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不愧是侦探先生　什么都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这只不过是基本中的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀　真少见啊　小香奈儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然趴在不认识人的膝盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香奈儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢猫咪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}PS:洒的东西请自行想象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点洒到外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　失礼了　我搞错地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀　你是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是整理书架的　你们认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那么小咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起　还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上　夫人　那个…我有些事想要问您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊…纪子　不　一定是纪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经知道我是续弦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎　是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从前妻纪子那里把柚木抢过来的事情也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎　是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事　反正也有这种传言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是被抢的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庞大的慰藉费和房子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这次又是小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下　您是说前妻把猫带走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这样　侦探先生　请您去搜索一下纪子的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.26,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌外人　她就一直一个人住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也经常不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探先生　拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳垢很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样　不要动…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人…夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　好厉害的饴耳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}饴耳:为一种疾病,体现为耳道很湿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思　麻烦您帮忙做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事　我自己要这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厉害…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次遇到挖耳朵挖得那么好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.60,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太夸张了　这是我的兴趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来您知道吗　是饴耳的话体味会很重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道不是世俗之说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么侦探先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下　饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是饴耳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以柚木一直没有什么好脸色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就加重了香水的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像栀子花香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚木说这个季节这个味道好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我其实并不是很喜欢很浓的香水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全被他改变了　被柚木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那家打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　我是干这行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近的拉面店看到过你　不自觉就和你打起招呼来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我不这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像故意瞄准这个时期而来打工的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美貌的寡妇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的保姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那栋房子肯定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不乘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘　还是不乘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么突然有兴趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是因为这是工作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是犯罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜入人家的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说的这么难听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在她不在的时候去找找猫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经足以构成犯罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一下明天开始我带薪休假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始在青户有重要的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是让我一个人去找猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这附近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银能追踪到的　只有到这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你契约的代价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装成自杀的杀人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要感谢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也差点被他附身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的能力和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能转移到其他身体里去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有对动物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是从人到人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　天一放晴就这么热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪子不在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说运气好还是运气不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　请问您要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘的东西…忘的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　是那个家伙　在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫　有妨碍　别把视线离开契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了吗　猫　猫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个男人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他难道知道寡妇和前妻的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪子家好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下　我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和这个屋子的人认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊　不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家　很让人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个啦　垃圾屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然跟区政府说过　但总不来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,420元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.40,0:21:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.23,0:21:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙　区区一只小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写成五月雨的梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}五月雨：日语中意为梅雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的雨水渗入我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.71,0:23:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栀子花的香气仿佛在窃笑我跟踪的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.51,0:23:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寡妇　这美妙的名词
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.05,0:23:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　为什么你是寡妇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.05,0:23:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起你那绝妙的挠耳朵技术我的心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.50,0:23:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你振作一点　老板
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.53,0:24:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再被那个女人的色相迷惑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你会被骗得一塌糊涂的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}本句是谚语,直译的话,意思是：你屁股上的毛都会被拔光的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.06,0:24:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹也是个女人　不要随便说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:09.23,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,350)\fs38}第八话　山栀子香散五月雨…（后篇）


